  <div class="bg-white border-b" style="border-color:rgba(28,16,8,.08)">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-2.5 breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="mx-1.5">›</span><span>Disclaimer</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <h1 class="section-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-2" style="color:#1c1008">Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="text-xs mb-8" style="color:rgba(28,16,8,.4);font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif">Last updated: December 10, 2024</p>
    <div class="prose-hm">
      <p>This page contains Harmonium Halt's Disclaimer for the website <a href="https://www.harmoniumhalt.com">www.harmoniumhalt.com</a>.</p>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Harmonium Halt is a free educational platform dedicated to teaching harmonium online. By using our website, you agree to these terms. Our content is for personal, non-commercial educational use.</p>
